<br>
Shiden, my dark elf that I have once again revived for who knows how long, doesn't really have much of a preference on where he sleeps, but I do make trips just to go to The Maiden's Fancy and give gold to the dancing girl, and he talks to Ratraz at least in passing.  He can also be found scribbling in a journal when he's alone, and when unoccupied he is fond of touring Lavastorm and Befallen.  When, before his last deletion, he moved to Echo Caverns to escape the wrath of the Lodge of the Dead, he would usually sleep in this one particular house in the back of the Fordel Quarter of Shadowhaven, and elsetimes in Echo Cavern itself, with the General, but I was always afraid of being attacked.<br>
